{"title":"阅读过百，更新下一篇","uid":"9afab0e25461b8a0c1df8a61db88db35","slug":"up主点赞","date":"2021-09-29T05:20:08.000Z","updated":"2021-10-04T11:10:52.947Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/up主点赞.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://p.qlogo.cn/zc_icon/0/d26af3d79b7891e83981d3e2635a618f163289918298/0.jpeg","content":"<p>最近，我关注的某几个<code>大</code>UP在视频最后会以点赞过万，立马更新下一集结尾.</p>\n<p>求赞的方法又多了一种！</p>\n<p>之前听到的一种方式无非就是如果喜欢本视频的话，欢迎点赞关注分享。<br>这没什么，up主在结尾提醒一下点赞，我都会根据喜好点个赞，或者精彩的投币，或者绝佳的收藏。<br>还有就是点赞的都有女朋友，明天会有好事发生。这也没什么。</p>\n<p>但是，慢慢的有些大up主看自己视频做到不错，观众热情很高。在结尾会说，点赞过**万，立马更新下一期。<br>不上刚上线的当然是立马点赞，这种观众和UP双赢的方法诚然没什么问题。但是细细一想，又觉得哪里不对。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>[周杰伦学习UP主的套路？INS点赞过20万，才能有新歌听(<a href=\"https://k.sina.cn/article_7548527386_p1c1ed631a001012n0o.html)]\">https://k.sina.cn/article_7548527386_p1c1ed631a001012n0o.html)]</a>.</p></blockquote>\n<p>还有令人尴尬的插入恰饭广告的视频也越来越多了。<br>牛逼的up能让内容和恰饭广告天衣无缝的衔接在一起<br>但有些up就会弄的非常尴尬，突然画风突变的插入恰饭推广，搞得体验非常差。</p>\n<p>这种矛盾需要一种解决方案。</p>\n<p>签约平台就不错，可以专心做内容。</p>\n<hr>\n\n<h2 id=\"2233-娘\"><a href=\"#2233-娘\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2233 娘\"></a><center>2233 娘</h2><p><img src=\"https://p.qlogo.cn/zc_icon/0/208ce8d24b0a38597e351198092c2b8516328991818414/0.jpeg\" alt=\"1.jpeg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://p.qlogo.cn/zc_icon/0/82e9bc23789f11c6ba38d28524ce56e216328991824013/0.jpg\" alt=\"2.jpg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://p.qlogo.cn/zc_icon/0/558b6a74a6ff8c953e08171423d5292e16328992193088/0.jpeg\" alt=\"3.jpeg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://p.qlogo.cn/zc_icon/0/42e409d6c4a5648c75bbbcae1b4a837916328991823634/0.jpeg\" alt=\"4.jpeg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://p.qlogo.cn/zc_icon/0/7195e3751f07ef0a47bcb63606458ca816328991834201/0.png\" alt=\"5.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://p.qlogo.cn/zc_icon/0/389e1ef4c1af7fa478535530870274ec16328991834359/0.jpeg\" alt=\"6.jpeg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://p.qlogo.cn/zc_icon/0/9704f804ead263c9313d818f2d4d014216328991834267/0.jpeg\" alt=\"7.jpeg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://p.qlogo.cn/zc_icon/0/d26af3d79b7891e83981d3e2635a618f163289918298/0.jpeg\" alt=\"8.jpeg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://p.qlogo.cn/zc_icon/0/52825c6ce14416ae6128f9fc3bc3aa3916328991827309/0.jpeg\" alt=\"9.jpeg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://p.qlogo.cn/zc_icon/0/41e6cb5467507d7b7a48c32168a7b98016328991829343/0.jpeg\" alt=\"10.jpeg\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"